1951;;Lorna Doone;;American;;Phil Karlson;;Barbara Hale, Richard Greene;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lorna_Doone_(1951_film);;Lorna Doone falls for John Ridd, but is betrothed (against her will) to one Carver Doone. As the English Civil War looms, John is determined to defeat the vicious Doone family and win Lorna over.